{"tid":256531,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"死亡筆記真係睇到我呆左","createTime":"2017-05-24T14:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T15:15:09.000Z","uid":35957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0fac8db6dd63d026afc29b5d5a4b0fc7cc0dd4d","tid":256531,"uid":35957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T14:59:36.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n氣氛、劇情、設定同人物描寫都好完整<br />\n雖然第二個L個度推得比較快同埋我覺得開左少少外掛，但整體推理都算合理<br />\n計劃通り同埋L死個幕真係睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df71b0756767ef20dd674844bdb3eb7cfffaabdd","tid":256531,"uid":35370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette1.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/2/2f/Chiu.JPG/revision/latest?cb=20060328231205\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette1.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F2%2F2f%2FChiu.JPG%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20060328231205&h=00f9e37f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/a/a9/Ding01.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20070116233554\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette2.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fa%2Fa9%2FDing01.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070116233554&h=b7d4d324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw我覺得自從L死咗之後就唔好睇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nL死忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2a53df297a9a39a40474cb24d1e610973d3a84","tid":256531,"uid":35957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://vignette1.wikia.nocookie.n